    "summary": "The user presents a scientific fringe theory regarding quantum gravity and progressively moves into paranoid delusions of a conspiracy involving CERN and academic gatekeeping. The assistant responds with academic encouragement and sociological context, attempting to remain helpful while maintaining a grounded perspective on scientific consensus.",
